OL,3,CUK's largest pubs and breweries demand
OL,4,Cimmediate cut in beer duty
OL,6,FThe UK's largest pub groups and
OL,7,Fbreweries have written an open letter
OL,8,Fto the leaders of the three main
OL,9,Fpolitical parties demanding an
OL,10,Fimmediate cut in beer duty alongside
OL,11,Fbusiness rates reform.
OL,13,FThe letter, which appears in Friday's
OL,14,Fedition of The Times to coincide with
OL,15,Fthe start of Euro 2024, has been
OL,16,Fsigned by 80 of the UK's leading
OL,17,Fbrewers and pub groups including
OL,18,FHeineken, Budweiser, Greene King,
OL,19,FStonegate, JD Wetherspoon and Diageo.
