OL,6,FThey call for a cut in duty as a
OL,7,F"first step" towards bringing the UK
OL,8,Fin line with the European average and
OL,9,Fan "urgent radical reform" of business
OL,10,Frates.
OL,12,FThe Government has frozen beer duty
OL,13,Fsince 2020 and the current rate is in
OL,14,Fplace until February 2025.
OL,16,FThe letter reads: "For every three
OL,17,Fpounds spent in a pub, one pound goes
OL,18,Fstraight to the tax man.
