OL,3,CUK's largest pubs and breweries demand
OL,4,Cimmediate cut in beer duty
OL,6,FThe letter, written by Emma McClarkin,
OL,7,Fchief executive of the British Beer
OL,8,Fand Pub Association, whose members
OL,9,Fbrew 90% of the beer sold in the UK,
OL,10,Fadds: "Whilst there has been
OL,11,Frecognition and acknowledgement from
OL,12,Fsuccessive governments on the
OL,13,Fimportant role that pubs and brewers
OL,14,Fplay in our society, a step change is
OL,15,Frequired to secure its future and to
OL,16,Fpromote and celebrate such an
OL,17,Fintrinsic part of British life that
OL,18,Fbrings combined economic, social, and
OL,19,Fcultural value to almost every
OL,20,Fcommunity around the country.
