OL,6,F"The beer and pub sector is special,
OL,7,Fbut it does not need special favours `
OL,8,Fit needs fair recognition of its
OL,9,Funique value.
OL,11,F"It is, therefore, imperative that the
OL,12,Fnext government provides a sustainable
OL,13,Fand proportionate fiscal and
OL,14,Fregulatory framework that allows the
OL,15,Fsector to do what it does best; invest
OL,16,Fin our businesses and employees,
OL,17,Fembrace changing consumer taste and
OL,18,Fdemands, and provide the community
OL,19,Fhubs that are the crucial and often
OL,20,Finvisible glue to social cohesion.
